Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Return to the Womb of
    the Mother
By: Roger Bacon
---
Species are not transmuted, but their subject matter rather, therefore
the first work is to reduce the body into water, that is into mercury,
and this is called Solution, which is the foundation of the whole art.
